<br>
  About Wizzard grouping, I agree with you, and we all do know that some class are group oriented while other are not so liked.. This is why it is important to have good friend I think. But I really think Wizzy are important in EQ. <br>
<br>
  About Damage, as I said Wizzard are good damage dealer in a short time. A Wizzard will always overdamage a Rogue in a short time but in longer time Rogue will ovedamage Wizzard. It is all about class specificity and role. Melee damage dealer are here to assume a minimum damage dealing over the time, while class like Wizzard are here to make a fight as short as possible in some circumstance.<br>
<br>
  I think there is nothing to argue about it, it is just needed to know how to use all the capability of everyclass to be the most efficient. <br>
<br>
  All of this to say that the issue is not the damage dealing, but to say that Wizzard are a good class and they are needed.<br>
<br>
Humbly,<br>
